      <title>韩国公开命令部分下岗医生重返工作岗位</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-publicly-orders-some-doctors-who-walked-off-job-back-work-2024-03-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国政府周五晚间公开命令 13 名医生重返工作岗位，否则将面临处罚，其中至少有一些医生曾公开表示约 9,000 名医生因医疗系统改革计划而罢工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-publicly-orders-some-doctors-who-walked-off-job-back-work-2024-03-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 00:43:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚总理为补选期间的生活成本行动辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-pm-defends-action-cost-living-amid-by-election-2024-03-02/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周六，选民们在澳大利亚维多利亚州举行的补选中进行了投票，这被视为对总理安东尼·阿尔巴内塞处理全国生活成本压力的公投。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-pm-defends-action-cost-living-amid-by-election-2024-03-02/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 00:23:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据 The Information 报道，Meta 拒绝了谷歌的虚拟现实合作提议</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/meta-rebuffed-google-proposal-virtual-reality-tie-up-information-reports-2024-03-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据 The Information 周五报道，Meta Platforms 决定不与 Alphabet 合作，将谷歌的 Android XR 平台用于其虚拟和混合现实 Quest 耳机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/meta-rebuffed-google-proposal-virtual-reality-tie-up-information-reports-2024-03-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 14:21:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国贝莱德公司减持矿业公司多金属国际的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/us-fund-blackrock-reduces-stake-miner-polymetal-international-2024-03-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国投资公司贝莱德 (BlackRock) 周五表示，该公司已将其在贵金属生产商 Polymetal International 中的持股比例从 9.91% 减至 7.45%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/us-fund-blackrock-reduces-stake-miner-polymetal-international-2024-03-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 13:25:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波兰将于周六午夜结束与斯洛伐克的延长边境管制</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/poland-end-extended-border-controls-with-slovakia-midnight-saturday-2024-03-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰内政部表示，在穿越该边境地区的非法移民威胁有所下降后，波兰将于周六午夜结束与斯洛伐克的延长边境管制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/poland-end-extended-border-controls-with-slovakia-midnight-saturday-2024-03-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 11:21:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国警方因罢工而突袭医生协会</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/south-korea-police-launch-raid-doctors-association-over-walkout-2024-03-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国警方周五对韩国医学协会官员发起突袭，当局加大压力，要求结束实习医生抗议卫生系统改革计划的罢工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/south-korea-police-launch-raid-doctors-association-over-walkout-2024-03-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 10:51:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>碧桂园面临清算诉讼的压力，以推动债务重组谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/country-garden-faces-heat-liquidation-suit-get-cracking-debt-revamp-talks-2024-03-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些海外债权人、顾问和分析师表示，针对中国碧桂园提出的清算申请将加大这家陷入困境的开发商坐上谈判桌进行债务重组谈判的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/country-garden-faces-heat-liquidation-suit-get-cracking-debt-revamp-talks-2024-03-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 10:23:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国人权事务高级专员表示，必须切断缅甸军政府获取武器和现金的渠道</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/myanmar-juntas-access-arms-cash-must-be-cut-off-un-rights-chief-says-2024-03-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国人权事务高级专员周五表示，国际社会必须采取“有针对性的行动”，限制缅甸军政府获得武器、航空燃料和外汇，以防止其对其人民实施“暴行”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/myanmar-juntas-access-arms-cash-must-be-cut-off-un-rights-chief-says-2024-03-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 09:55:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>缅甸市场炮击造成12人死亡、80人受伤——叛军民兵</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/artillery-shelling-kills-12-myanmar-market-injures-80-rebel-militia-2024-03-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在缅甸，炮弹落在若开邦西部一个繁忙的市场上，造成至少 12 名平民死亡，执政的军方和反军政府势力互相指责，指责该东南亚国家最近发生的暴力事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/artillery-shelling-kills-12-myanmar-market-injures-80-rebel-militia-2024-03-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 09:20:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚可能永久放弃对在海底电缆作业的外国船舶的规则</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysia-reinstates-cabotage-waiver-foreign-ships-undersea-cable-repair-2024-03-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚交通部长周五表示，马来西亚已决定推翻先前的决定，允许外国船只在其水域修复海底电缆，并补充称此举可能会永久化，以鼓励科技投资并支持数字经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/malaysia-reinstates-cabotage-waiver-foreign-ships-undersea-cable-repair-2024-03-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Mar 2024 07:49:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
